#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.randint.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.randint"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:1 of
msgid "Return random integers from `low` (inclusive) to `high` (exclusive)."
msgstr "从 `low`（包含）到 `high`（不包含）返回随机整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:3 of
msgid ""
"Return random integers from the \"discrete uniform\" distribution of the "
"specified dtype in the \"half-open\" interval [`low`, `high`). If `high` "
"is None (the default), then results are from [0, `low`)."
msgstr ""
"从指定 dtype 的“离散均匀”分布中，在“半开”区间 [`low`, `high`) 内返回"
"随机整数。如果 `high` 为 None（默认值），则结果来自 [0, `low`)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:7 of
msgid ""
"Lowest (signed) integer to be drawn from the distribution (unless "
"``high=None``, in which case this parameter is one above the *highest* "
"such integer)."
msgstr ""
"从分布中抽取的最小（有符号）整数（除非 ``high=None``，在这种情况下该参数"
"是 *最大* 整数加一）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:11 of
msgid ""
"If provided, one above the largest (signed) integer to be drawn from the "
"distribution (see above for behavior if ``high=None``)."
msgstr ""
"如果提供该参数，则表示从分布中抽取的最大（有符号）整数加一（如果 ``high="
"None``，请参见上文描述）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:14 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  Default is None, in which case a single value is"
" returned."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"默认为 None，此时返回单个值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:18 of
msgid ""
"Desired dtype of the result. All dtypes are determined by their name, "
"i.e., 'int64', 'int', etc, so byteorder is not available and a specific "
"precision may have different C types depending on the platform. The "
"default value is 'np.int'."
msgstr ""
"结果的期望数据类型。所有数据类型都由其名称决定，例如 'int64'、'int' 等，"
"因此不支持字节顺序，且特定精度在不同平台上可能有不同的 C 类型。默认值为 '"
"np.int'。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:23 of
msgid "if density specified, a sparse tensor will be created"
msgstr "如果指定了 density，将创建一个稀疏张量"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:25 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:27 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:29 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:32 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- `size`-shaped tensor of random integers from the appropriate "
"distribution, or a single such random int if `size` not provided."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 来自适当分布的 `size` 形状的随机整数张量，如果未提供 `size`，"
"则返回单个这样的随机整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`random.random_integers`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:39 of
msgid ""
"similar to `randint`, only for the closed interval [`low`, `high`], and 1"
" is the lowest value if `high` is omitted. In particular, this other one "
"is the one to use to generate uniformly distributed discrete non-"
"integers."
msgstr ""
"与 `randint` 类似，但用于闭区间 [`low`, `high`]，如果省略 `high`，则 1 是"
"最小值。特别是，这个函数用于生成均匀分布的离散非整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:42 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.randint.randint:50 of
msgid "Generate a 2 x 4 tensor of ints between 0 and 4, inclusive:"
msgstr "生成一个 2 x 4 的整数张量，数值在 0 到 4 之间（包含 0 和 4）："

